OL,3,CCare home shut down after inspections
OL,4,Cfound it 'unsafe and understaffed'
OL,6,FA care home in Kent has been shut down
OL,7,Fafter two inspections found it was
OL,8,Funsafe and posed a risk to residents.
OL,10,FBlossoms Care Home in Greenhithe
OL,11,Flooked after people with dementia and
OL,12,Flearning and physical disabilities.
OL,14,FBut the Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,15,Ffound that its staff were
OL,16,Fdirectionless, leadership was poor and
OL,17,Fthose living there were possibly at
OL,18,Frisk of harm. The watchdog shut it
OL,19,Fdown in November as a result.
