OL,3,CCare home shut down after inspections
OL,4,Cfound it 'unsafe and understaffed'
OL,6,FAcross a range of benchmarks, the
OL,7,Fwatchdog scored the home as either
OL,8,Finadequate or in need of improvement.
OL,9,FOverall, the CQC said the home had
OL,10,Fbreached five of the legal regulations.
OL,12,FAmong the issues was a lack of
OL,13,Fawareness of residents' weight-loss.
OL,14,FIn one case, the watchdog said a
OL,15,Fresident lost 10 kilos without any
OL,16,Fstaff noticing.
