OL,3,CCare home shut down after inspections
OL,4,Cfound it 'unsafe and understaffed'
OL,6,FIt wrote: "A visiting healthcare
OL,7,Fprofessional identified 1 person had
OL,8,Flost 10kg of weight in 2 months. Staff
OL,9,Fhad failed to identify this and seek
OL,10,Furgent medical attention."
OL,12,FElsewhere, the CQC criticised
OL,13,FBlossoms' staffing. "The provider did
OL,14,Fnot make sure there were enough
OL,15,Fqualified, skilled and experienced
OL,16,Fstaff," it wrote in its report. "They
OL,17,Fdid not work together well to provide
OL,18,Fsafe care that met people's individual
OL,19,Fneeds."
