OL,4,Cfound it 'unsafe and understaffed'
OL,6,FIt added: "The week before our
OL,7,Finspection, 2 people had gone into
OL,8,Fhospital. The NI told us they made the
OL,9,Fdecision to reduce staffing from 4 to
OL,10,F3 (...) We observed that there were
OL,11,Fnot sufficient numbers of staff. "
OL,13,FFurther problems emerged in the care
OL,14,Fthat was provided for people with
OL,15,Fepilepsy as well the cleanliness of
OL,16,Fthe home itself.
