OL,3,CCare home shut down after inspections
OL,4,Cfound it 'unsafe and understaffed'
OL,6,FThe watchdog noted: "The (nominated
OL,7,Findividual) told us they were unaware
OL,8,F3 people living at the service had
OL,9,Fepilepsy and confirmed that no staff
OL,10,Fhad received training in supporting
OL,11,Fpeople with epilepsy."
OL,13,FIt continued: "The service was not
OL,14,Fclean or well maintained in places to
OL,15,Fmake cleaning effective.
OL,17,F"Areas including people's rooms,
OL,18,Fhallways, communal areas were visibly
OL,19,Fdirty with stains of fluids down the
OL,20,Fwalls and floors, and marks on
OL,21,Fcarpets."
